


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_80c59c43:


    "莉莉在設定好前往文典星的航向後，幾乎立刻回到了自己的艙室。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_505c9ee8:


    "自記憶恢復後我再沒機會和她交談，我渴望能再次守在她身旁。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_33d60539:


    "我叩響她的房門，過了片刻她才將門微微推開一道縫隙。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_9bf4cec7:


    l "噢，是你啊。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_8d9a290d:


    "不像我希望的那樣受歡迎啊..."


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_3fc15ae0:


    c "你還好嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_c54a2cf5:


    l "沒事，只是剛才睡着了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_720b290f:


    c "能理解，大概是他們注射藥物的殘留作用。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_294f22da:


    l "也許吧。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_72ca6120:


    c "介意我進來嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_4dc06892:


    l "我很累了，[p_name_short]。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_278090a3:


    c "我知道，但我們得談談牢房裡發生的事。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_2974d059:


    l "牢房裡發生了什麼？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_ccc65adf:


    c "你知道的...{w}我們之間..."


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_cbe608f7:


    c "你不記得了？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_7e8fc039:


    l "不記得。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_933c72df:


    c "可是..."


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_84df278e:


    l "我現在真的只想睡覺。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_7a61c004:


    "沒等我再說第二句話，她已經闔上了門。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_5fda5328:


    "和她在一起這麼久，我只是想知道她還好嗎。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_5d88433f:


    "我輕敲她的房門，過了會兒她打開了門。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_0dde56ac:


    l "噢，嘿 [p_name_short]。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_144ef471:


    l "剛剛不小心睡着了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_2b91f690:


    c "可能是他們注射的藥物還在起作用。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_4b9e0353:


    c "你還好嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_d37a2cb7:


    l "我覺得還行。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_0c3e045f:


    l "目前都沒做夢。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_d480f87a:


    c "聽你這麼說我就放心了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_9fd85fd4:


    c "如果有變化，你知道去哪兒找我。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_lilly_talk_9876f704:


    l "我知道，謝謝[p_name_short]。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_1e93475b:


    c "嘿，你還挺得住嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_156a10ae:


    av "勉強撐着。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_ac800281:


    av "真是一團糟。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_be6000d9:


    c "是啊，完全沒想過會成這樣。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_01e5f10e:


    av "我也是，說真的現在我沒法處理這些事。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_2bffb07d:


    av "我們逃出來前約好要談談的，確實應該..."


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_59ce1471:


    av "但現在不行，[p_name_short]希望你能理解。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_29a4599a:


    c "不，我不理解。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_4298a054:


    c "這堆破事必須現在解決。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_9868b26f:


    av "不，沒必要。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_3ec23c7a:


    av "等我們倆都消化完這些事再說吧，免得說出讓彼此後悔的話。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_22b5d7f4:


    av "對不起，[p_name_short]。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_1334c24f:


    c "但至少回答我這個問題：在空間站的事你還記得多少？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_4a10551b:


    c "我是指恢復記憶前那段。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_a384e4c0:


    av "記得很清楚。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_a30bcba3:


    av "突然問這個幹嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_361d55ac:


    c "莉莉說她完全不記得了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_354cbe27:


    av "也許藥效對每個人的情況都不同？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_13251290:


    c "也許吧。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_81e97d6d:


    av "或者她只是不想談論這件事。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_2c72b826:


    c "這聽起來耳熟..."


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_3de72580:


    av "別這麼他媽的發牢騷。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_d7269434:


    c "我覺得我是。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_5e1580a8:


    av "等我們兩個這該死的思維混亂都好一點之後，再看看我們立場如何，好吧？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_88df38a7:


    c "同意。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_7b186832:


    c "有件事一直困擾着我，你能想起我們在站上時的任何事嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_4a10551b_1:


    c "我是說，在我們恢復記憶之前。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_a384e4c0_1:


    av "是的，我能，猶在眼前。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_a30bcba3_1:


    av "你爲什麼提這個？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_361d55ac_1:


    c "莉莉說她什麼都不記得。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_354cbe27_1:


    av "也許藥效對每個人的情況都不同？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_13251290_1:


    c "也許吧。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_81e97d6d_1:


    av "或者她只是不想談論這件事。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_c8cf5b1d:


    c "我也這樣想過。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_e1992d7a:


    av "我肯定她最終會回心轉意的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_257af806:


    av "不過你們確實有很多要談的，我認爲你們真的應該談一談，等你們都準備好後。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_940e6c24:


    av "這整個旅程就是一場巨大的精神衝擊。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_61ed7c35:


    c "你說得太對了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_2f30cf04:


    av "如果你需要我，我就在這裡。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_5cd7eb66:


    c "謝謝，我會記住的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_dce3ca41:


    av "晚安，[p_name_short]。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_0850efde:


    c "晚安，艾文。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_1e93475b_1:


    c "嘿，你還好嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_156a10ae_1:


    av "勉強撐得住。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_ac800281_1:


    av "真是亂七八糟。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_be6000d9_1:


    c "是啊，這和我想象的完全不一樣。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_01e5f10e_1:


    av "我也是，說實話，我現在真的沒法處理這一切。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_2bffb07d_1:


    av "我們答應過逃跑後要談談，我們真的應該..."


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_59ce1471_1:


    av "只是不是現在，[p_name_short]，我希望你理解。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_29a4599a_1:


    c "不，我不理解。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_4298a054_1:


    c "我們現在就得解決這個爛攤子。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_9868b26f_1:


    av "不，我們不用。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_3ec23c7a_1:


    av "等我們都消化完這一切再說，除非我們可能說些以後會後悔的話。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_22b5d7f4_1:


    av "對不起，[p_name_short]。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_d7269434_1:


    c "我想是吧。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_5e1580a8_1:


    av "等我們都處理完這整個腦子亂糟糟的狀況，再看看我們的立場，好嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_88df38a7_1:


    c "同意。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_dce3ca41_1:


    av "晚安，[p_name_short]。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_0850efde_1:


    c "晚安，艾文。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_1e93475b_2:


    c "嘿，你還好嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_1bbb321f:


    av "我很好，謝謝你問起。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_db1c8842:


    c "我只是在想，你記得我們在空間站時的任何事嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_4a10551b_2:


    c "我是說，在我們恢復記憶之前。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_a384e4c0_2:


    av "是的，我記得很清楚。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_a30bcba3_2:


    av "你爲什麼提起這個？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_361d55ac_2:


    c "莉莉說她什麼都不記得。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_354cbe27_2:


    av "也許藥效對每個人的情況都不同？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_13251290_2:


    c "可能吧。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_81e97d6d_2:


    av "或者她可能只是不想談論這事。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_c8cf5b1d_1:


    c "我也這樣想過。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_e1992d7a_1:


    av "我肯定她最終會想通的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_257af806_1:


    av "雖然你們確實有很多要聊的，而且我覺得你們一旦都準備好了就應該聊聊。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_940e6c24_1:


    av "這整個旅途就是個巨大的精神衝擊。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_61ed7c35_1:


    c "你說得太對了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_2f30cf04_1:


    av "如果你需要我，我在這兒。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_aven_talk_5cd7eb66_1:


    c "謝謝，我會記住的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_7bb1d557:


    c "我想知道我們能不能談談。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_94584b6c:


    ra "如果是關於研究站上發生的事，別擔心，我現在沒事了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_e7fcde5d:


    c "我知道你沒事了，但我想知道你在那兒到底發生了什麼。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_d52af839:


    ra "爲什麼？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_3b38004d:


    c "因爲我不希望你感到那麼痛苦。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_0a55e903:


    c "研究站上有些東西勾起你沉重的情緒，我不想你覺得自己得獨自承受這一切。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_1c8447a2:


    ra "你之前說過了，我相信你。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_3db0fda6:


    ra "我...{w} 我真的不知道從哪裡開始。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_60f07ac9:


    c "爲什麼不從頭開始？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_0b08417b:


    ra "那可能最好。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_e0f915e4:


    ra "我承了我母親的名字，她叫蕾。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_5a524f25:


    ra "那是一個我自豪的名字。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_a19d90bc:


    ra "在我們的世界裡，女人大多被視爲必要的邪惡，因爲她們能生育。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_114fca97:


    ra "除此之外，她們過着隱居的生活，不參與日常生活。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_3039a634:


    ra "她們供那些統治銅綠星的男人取樂，我父親是頭兒。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_34122355:


    ra "我出生時有個不同的名字，我父親至今還用那個名字叫我。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_b0588090:


    ra "他非常高興我母親給他生了個兒子，因爲繼承人能保障我們的血統。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_08acbde8:


    ra "從我剛能說話起，我就讓他失望了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_b0ca5e2e:


    ra "我從來都不是他想要的兒子，甚至他需要的兒子，內心深處我一直是蕾妮。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_f7645069:


    c "真高興你決定告訴我。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_b9bd751b:


    c "很多事情現在開始豁然開朗了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_0d98f346:


    c "就像在研究站的更衣室裏你的行爲，不得不穿那些男人的衣服。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_4b45f7c9:


    ra "我知道那看起來挺徒勞的，考慮到我們在那兒對抗的是什麼。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_raene_talk_700cc746:


    ra "但那一切都突然湧上心頭。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_bbeadae7:


    c "你和基芙的關係不是巧合，對吧？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_260b614d:


    ra "是的，我曾設法聯繫上她的人民，當代表團訪問銅綠星時。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_878a6986:


    ra "倫科伊族的無性別性質在整個星系都廣爲人知。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_858ea150:


    c "我也有所耳聞。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_e121f9de:


    c "考慮到我聽說的關於你們星球的事，與倫科伊族代表團的會面肯定挺尷尬吧？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_e1ca33f2:


    ra "我很確定，但\"神祕會\"或多或少被迫與他們打交道，是對其他政治派別的禮遇。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_9fc8d6bc:


    ra "當然，那次會面毫無結果。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_49ae367a:


    c "\"神祕會\"？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_71480290:


    ra "是的，我星球上的智者統治議會，我父親是他們的領袖。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_f5f7c27d:


    c "好吧。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_eb9898d8:


    c "所以基芙的人民設法把你帶走並藏起來？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_7d9bb1a7:


    ra "是的，藏了一段時間，在你們和基芙接我們上去之前。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_5ac988ca:


    ra "在銅綠星藏匿期間，他們爲我準備了變性過程。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_16112d2f:


    ra "最終是基芙在\"私生子\"號上進行了第一次治療。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_88d6a371:


    ra "但你大概早猜到啦。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_e1ce0fba:


    c "之前在空間站上你可是心神不寧得很。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_5fbce80e:


    ra "是啊。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_2ca55ef4:


    ra "其實挺傻的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_3fd5b21a:


    c "你老這麼說，可我完全不覺得這事傻。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_fd85e2e5:


    ra "就是當時我從儲物艙醒來，我們倆火急火燎的，後來才意識到他們給我穿了和你一樣的衣服。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_d8714f78:


    ra "當然了，他們可能看到了我兩腿間那玩意兒，但那一刻所有情緒都湧了上來。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_5991bba3:


    ra "剛意識到自己還有好長的路要走呢。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_c19e5dee:


    c "你已經進步很大了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_e9a2064c:


    c "在那情形下離開家鄉，開始接受基芙的治療..."


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_50b1f720:


    ra "我知道。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_1caaa7af:


    ra "以後還會有更多這種時刻，我希望到時候我能準備好面對。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_9104ab2e:


    c "肯定會有的，但千萬別因爲別人怎麼待你或看你而懷疑自己。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_3d324c1b:


    c "而且你知道如果這事讓你受傷了，我永遠在你身邊。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_86f8ed97:


    ra "謝謝[p_name_short]，這話對我太重要了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_10b6bb9b:


    c "困難可能會有，但我信你搞得定。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_85994e5e:


    c "作出選擇本身就是勇敢之舉，顯真本色。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_ee110576:


    ra "大概吧。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_3a156c81:


    c "你提到蕾，你母親，她知道你試圖逃離銅綠星的事嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_e6045e45:


    ra "不...{w}那個...{w}我本該告訴你的..."


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_e06ccc24:


    ra "我母親在我不到五歲時候就去世了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_a92b1aa5:


    c "噢...{w}真替你難過。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_9797f186:


    ra "我留着些她的記憶和一張珍藏的照片。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_9bd6e686:


    ra "她在我童年裡不是持續的存在，因爲女人只被允許提供孩子必要的照料，剩下的都是男人的義務。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_e64bfe0f:


    ra "至少對兒子們來說是這樣，女兒們會被帶到母親們被關押的地方去。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_6ba3bd9b:


    c "聽起來很糟糕，說實話。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_f8bf3472:


    ra "確實是。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_3776b25a:


    ra "在五歲時我還是會失去母親的，因爲撫養完全落到父親們身上了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_84d1348c:


    ra "我母親在我四歲生日後幾周就生病了，並在一年內去世了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_cd1f940e:


    ra "我父親，或者說他僱用的員工，從那以後就一直照顧我。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_5d1af5a5:


    c "我不知道該說什麼......"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_21c90538:


    c "多麼糟糕的童年啊。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_cb9e98d8:


    ra "也不全是壞的，但我不會稱之爲快樂的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_bf557386:


    c "不，一點也不。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_08f5f554:


    c "你告訴我你父親仍然把你當作兒子看待？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_54b82b74:


    ra "他是這樣的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_fc8acdcf:


    ra "他可能以爲還能改變我...{w}治癒我..."


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_f5f7c27d_1:


    c "對。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_ed91716b:


    c "你認爲他想那樣做是出於父母錯誤的愛，還是有更多因素在起作用？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_b777ee1b:


    ra "部分是吧，我想。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_3d01fa5b:


    ra "我父親是個非常謹慎的人，他根本不表露感情，所以很難知道他想要我什麼。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_8c6d1ec5:


    ra "大祭司的頭銜不是世襲的，但它已經在我家族中傳了好幾代了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_ebfa7dec:


    ra "在我成爲越來越大的尷尬之前，他可能曾把我看作他的接班人。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_d56e0766:


    ra "現在我都不確定他是想拯救我，還是控制我可能對他聲譽造成的損害。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_9cb18faa:


    c "不管怎麼說都聽起來是錯誤的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_cecfb499:


    ra "確實，不是嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_3b03e983:


    c "我很高興你向我傾訴，蕾妮。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_dd7f0223:


    ra "說實話，和你聊天感覺很好。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_7621fe6d:


    ra "謝謝，[p_name]。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_4a382f8f:


    c "睡個好覺，蕾妮。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_5325db35:


    ra "你也是，[p_name_short]。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_2e8a5462:


    c "我猜也是。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_6e99eab9:


    c "嗯，你知道的，我不介意。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_aa81d120:


    ra "我很高興聽到你這麼說。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_dca103f9:


    c "基芙在治療你，我猜？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_047226c2:


    ra "是的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_9db97ba1:


    c "好，我希望你在這裡感到受歡迎，也希望你能繼續這樣。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_ec8c4954:


    ra "呃...{w} 是的，我也希望如此。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_54c8f013:


    c "睡個好覺。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_393c8561:


    ra "你也是。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_7621fe6d_1:


    ra "謝謝，[p_name]。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_9f624f4f:


    ra "但我現在沒事了，真的沒事。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_7b314c8d:


    c "既然你這麼說，你知道你隨時可以找我聊天。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_5f8fa3c2:


    c "因爲，作爲這艘船的指揮官，我有權知道。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_2ce55b1e:


    ra "我可以向你保證，現在一切正常。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_76badc88:


    ra "真的，再也不會發生了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_ra_conversation_c1bfa14d:


    c "既然你這麼說..."


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_7fa66814:


    "自從我們登上\"私生子\"號以來，我的心思就一直飄向伊娃。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_bb0c7f60:


    "我很害怕回到模擬器裏去，尤其是想到我們已經離開差不多六個月了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_28573bc5:


    "就在離開巴蘭西斯星前，我已經把莉莉的檔案加載進系統了，但我找不到一個安靜的時機真正進入模擬。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_65e7d1c6:


    "我發現自己身處花園裡，那座小橋上，她上次就是在這裡道別的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_8a8aeeb1:


    "帶着一種強烈的預感，我朝房子走去。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_c2ad8b4f:


    "門廊不見人影，莉莉也不在，我便進了屋。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_b3e5f9d5:


    c "伊娃？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_7df34f95:


    c "莉莉？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_e9ca02e1:


    c "我回來啦。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_281c0e8b:


    "樓下所有房間靜悄悄的。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_04593336:


    "壁爐裏的火早就滅透了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_91d6b504:


    "我上樓走向伊娃和莉莉的臥室。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_fc3b7962:


    c "你們在嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_bc6ff73c:


    c "耽擱這麼久才回來實在抱歉，但事情我可以解釋。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_b3e5f9d5_1:


    c "伊娃？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_a2cfab58:


    "就在這時伊娃的房門咣當大開，怒氣衝衝的莉莉闖進走廊。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_7a9139c4:


    l "你他媽能不能閉嘴？！"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_465204c9:


    l "她不想見你，這還不夠清楚嗎？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_166c87f0:


    l "她每天念叨你，擔心你遭遇不測。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_6049a68a:


    l "明明約好在家碰頭，結果消失好幾個月。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_dc100a14:


    l "你怎麼能這樣拋下她？"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_8da22fa0:


    "莉莉這般敵意讓我心驚肉跳。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_d327f849:


    "在\"康維泰\"研究站親密相處後，我認識的她根本不是這樣。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_4bbe92ab:


    c "我...{w}我可以解釋。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_435f9ef0:


    l "解釋你當然會解釋。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_c0ab2ba7:


    l "但我們沒興趣聽。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_57b9b7e1:


    l "離我們遠點，[p_name_short]，你禍害得夠夠的了。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_718cf82c:


    "她當面甩上房門，留我愣在走廊裏。"


translate traditional_chinese ep006_eva_talk_7938e2fb:


    "我立刻退出模擬倉衝回房間，抓狂地想着操他媽的到底還能怎麼挽回。"

